{"tid":899981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大茶飯] 央媒披露 「中國製造2025」經費分配","createTime":"2018-11-13T01:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T16:38:39.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c7072b85654e9fed815334e54af7b7a8a9bc2e98","tid":899981,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:13:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">央媒披露 「中國製造2025」經費分配</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2206840/%E5%A4%AE%E5%AA%92%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%20%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A02025%E3%80%8D%E7%B6%93%E8%B2%BB%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2206840%2F%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2%2520%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A02025%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%25B6%2593%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2585%258D&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1905f95c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2206840/%E5%A4%AE%E5%AA%92%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%20%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A02025%E3%80%8D%E7%B6%93%E8%B2%BB%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】月底習特會前，美國總統特朗普日前稱，中國已放棄中美貿易戰觸發點之一的「中國製造2025」計劃，然而，內地官媒昨披露國家重點研發經費分配情況，高新技術約佔總經費的3成，即40億元（人民幣，下同）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高新技術佔總經費約3成<br />\n<br />\n</span>新華社旗下《經濟參考報》引述中國科技部消息，截至目前，中國今年國家重點研發計劃共計立項640項，429個單位共獲得127億元國撥經費的資助，涉及社會發展、高新技術、農林科技以及基礎研究4大領域的38個專項。<br />\n<br />\n具體來看，2018年度國家重點研發計劃經費分別在社會發展和高新技術投入50億元和40億元，佔年度總經費的40%和30%；農業領域投入保持穩定，2018年農林科技新批項目近100項，經費20億元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">值得注意，加強社會監控、應對公共突發事件的「公共安全風險防控與應急技術裝備專項」本年度共有55個項目獲資助，經費約12.8億元，為所有專項中最多。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另新能源汽車也獲得愈來愈多重視，共獲得10億元經費資助，主要投入電池和電機研究。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述專家分析，隨着創新驅動國家戰略的深入推進和科技體制改革紅利逐漸釋放，智能製造、農林科技、生物醫藥研發等領域，將在中央財政的扶持下迅猛發展。"},{"pid":"fe71deac4a85a664657da8552dd585cfd637acbb","tid":899981,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbd3830dd241ee03068a60e42c8ed774a80d38a","tid":899981,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:23:36.000Z","msg":"講咁耐得百幾億 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"c44d0a2543e2c21716ba257be68e529399b9284d","tid":899981,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efbd3830dd241ee03068a60e42c8ed774a80d38a","tid":899981,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:23:36.000Z","msg":"講咁耐得百幾億 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:27:50.000Z","msg":"呢D只係見得光既部份, 當然少啦, 唔通俾錢偷技術既錢都講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57693e39ce6df09d43b76bd8c6d00bbb77ed973f","tid":899981,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c74c1e0dc07555ef5e69dc630b778bf93a7fda1","tid":899981,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一百幾億就可以中国製造2025<br />\n咁一萬億科左上去可以有咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71762cc8e43722a6f4127c8031854935a3b04a24","tid":899981,"uid":37757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T16:38:39.000Z","msg":"一萬億填海仲話必須<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}